        public static Supplier<Point> createOffsetGenerator​(int gridSize,
                                                    boolean down)
        Parameters:
        gridSize - difference x, y, or both, between offset points in pixels,
        down - Direction of traversing.
        Returns:
        generator of a sequence of points which are offset from the initial point for positioning of a rectangle. This implementation returns a sequence of offsets which form concentric half-circles up or down.
